      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the warnings. i turned everything off at the breaker like you said. i went out there and looked, and i think i saw some dust and maybe some debris stuck near the motor area, but nothing too crazy. do you think it could be something like a capacitor that went bad? i heard people mention that online when the motor hums but wont start.",
